This paper is about object detection using deep convolutional neural networks, which is a popular topic in computer vision (CV) research. Therefore, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a novel approach to improve the efficiency of region proposal generation, which involves training a model using deep learning techniques. This suggests that the paper may also be relevant to sub-categories such as cs.LG (machine learning), cs.AI (artificial intelligence), and cs.NE (neural and evolutionary computing). Finally, the paper involves empirical studies to evaluate the proposed method, which may fall under the sub-category cs.MM (multimedia).
